WRESTLING ADVERTISING CIMS has recently ventured into uncharted territories by bringing your hard releases directly to the ultimate fan base: WRESTLING FANS. Each account places ads on some or all of these prime time cable wrestling shows: USA's WWF Monday Night Raw, TNT's WCW Monday Nitro, UPN Thursday Smackdown, ECW Friday Night on TNT and TBS's WCW Wednesday Thunder. These top-rated programs deliver prime, reactive audiences for your more aggressive releases. Contact Scott Register (reg@cimsmusic.com) at CIMS HQ (205.879.9023x203) for more info. COST: $11,000<br>
<br>
