LISTENING BOOTH PROGRAM This program is designed to place a listening booth position in the majority of stores that are members of The Coalition of Independent Music Stores. Each store has been equipped with a 20-disc wall listening booth that is printed with the CIMS logo, and whose space is totally devoted to those titles featured in the program. Each listening booth will have merchandise displayed along with a common poster that includes cover art and biographical information about each artist and the CIMS logo. Structured in response to labels' needs in marketing new and developing artists, it offers the opportunity to place titles in a listening booth setting with CIMS stores at an attractive price. This comprehensive effort has been designed not only to be simple, but also cost-effective and timesaving, and to enhance awareness in the stores most known to expose your artists. Unlike other listening booth programs, the retailer will get the bulk of the money to encourage compliance and attractive pricing. Effective 4/19/00, there are 51 stores participating; however, this number fluctuates as new members are added to CIMS.<br>
 Cost per slot/per store: $60а а а а Total cost per slot: $3060.00 ($60 x 51 Stores)<br>
Total buy-in per slot: 12 units/store, min.а а а а Time duration: 1 calendar month<br>
